title: Oxford Advanced Learners Dictionary 8th Edition for Windows
description:
This is the portable edition. You can run it from anywhere. No need to install. 

How to run:

1. This software is compressed in 7zip format. So you will need either 7zip or WinRAR to decompress (extract).

2. Extract OALD8.7z using either 7zip or WInRAR.

3. Then open the extracted OALD8 folder.

4. Here you will find the executable "oald8.exe" file. 
image

5. Double click "oald8.exe" and your Oxford Dictionary will open up.
image

6. Enjoy ! 

100% NO VIRUS and NO PASSWORDS !!!!!!!
